---
description: Nest server — module API types live in .interface.ts files
globs: packages/server/**/*.ts
---

# No inline module API types

- Put shared interfaces and DTO-shaped types for a module in **`*.interface.ts`** files colocated with that module.
- Avoid large inline `interface` / `type` definitions inside `*.service.ts` or `*.controller.ts` for anything that defines the module’s public contract.
- Re-export or import from `@planning-monefica/shared-types` when the contract is cross-cutting.
